\v 28 \x - \xo 12:28 \xt Lk 10.25-28\x*AŇčakwan gen teban yoy…®Ňčdet am…®n k…®nda da ab…®Ňč p…®ndakban Yesu gat Sadyusi am…®n gat gen emat awit. Yesu da gen kobog…® tag…®si yoy…®Ňčban nandaŇček Yesu yaŇč iy…®g…®t, ‚ÄúNi gen teban da gen teban morap yapmaŇč mudaŇček mib…®ltok asak?‚ÄĚ
